skills/rhei-state-machine-writer/SKILL.md:237:- `rhei next` will refuse to claim a task if any `inputs:` file for the current state is missing, and prints an explicit missing-artifact error.
skills/rhei-state-machine-writer/SKILL.md:238:- `rhei transition` and `rhei complete` will refuse to leave a state if any `outputs:` file has not been written.
