docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md:683:- **`rhei run`** evaluates success or failure and performs the state transition.
docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md:684:- **Callbacks** handle side effects of that transition (creating artifacts, spawning tasks, notifying systems).
