docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md:835:Timeout transitions are declared in the `transitions` array with the `timeout` field. The existing `timeout` field in the transition schema (see [Transitions Specification](rhei-transitions.spec.md#transition-definition)) is used by `rhei run` to determine what to do when an agent times out.
