docs/specs/rhei-programs.spec.md:315:Program states use the same `inputs` / `outputs` artifact contracts as any other state — see [States Specification — Artifact Contracts](rhei-states.spec.md#artifact-contracts) for the schema, path template variables, and general semantics.
