docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md:875:Not every state can be completed directly via `rhei complete`. The command requires a non-cancelled terminal state reachable in one hop:
docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md:878:- From `agent-review-fix`: no direct path to `completed` exists. The agent must transition to `agent-review` first, then complete from there.
