docs/comparison.md:16:| **Custom / pluggable state machine** | Yes — YAML state machine, `node_policy`, profiles, artifact contracts, callbacks | No — fixed `open`/`in_progress`/`closed` (+ `blocked`, `deferred`) | Configurable statuses (data, no semantics) | No (4 states, prompt-enforced) | No (3 states) | No | No | No (mode-switching is the FSM) | No (internal) | No (`todo`/`in_progress`/`finished`/`cancelled`) |
