docs/comparison.md:18:| **Ready-work selection** | `rhei next` — terminal-state `Prior:` + node-policy filter | `bd ready` — transitive closed-deps query | Implied (no dedicated command yet) | LLM picks from list | LLM picks | LLM picks | User picks | Orchestrator picks subtask | Scheduler over DAG | LLM picks |
docs/comparison.md:19:| **Concurrency model** | Directory Workspace: per-task files, global graph merge; atomic CAS via `rhei transition` | Hash-IDs, Dolt cell-merge, atomic `--claim` | Worktree-based parallel agents | None — per-session | None | None | None | Sequential (parent suspends) | Internal scheduling | Coordinator + Specialists |
