+### SMT-004: Gating and Terminal Behavior
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md` -> `Per-state fields`, `States`, `Completion paths`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md` -> `State Definition`, `Wildcard Semantics`
