+### SMT-007: Artifact Contracts
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md` -> `Artifact Contracts`, `Optional Inputs`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md` -> `State Definition`, `Artifact Enforcement`
